Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.01,0:22:56.10,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}{\fad(250,250)}The kindness that he once saw is now gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.10,0:23:06.90,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}{\fad(250,0)}He steps forward alone, looking only at his feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.90,0:23:22.29,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}{\fad(250,0)\3c&HCB6D14&\bord2\blur2}He always listened to the song that disappeared by morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.29,0:23:38.18,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}{\fad(0,500)}He chased forever those footprints we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sora,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I dreamed about someone I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.89,0:00:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san really did come back after everything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.47,0:00:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He gave me something important, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.78,0:00:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.16,0:00:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't give up on something like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.25,0:00:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.54,0:00:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do my best, even by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.54,0:02:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I'm going to try to go outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,even though walking is painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.28,0:02:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's rest a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.42,0:02:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll get this,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.54,0:02:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the weird juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that person,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.71,0:02:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the one who was living with us until a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.91,0:03:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems vaguely familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So the freeloader left?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he'll eventually come back if he has nowhere else to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.51,0:03:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a hard time too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I was trying my best so that you could stay here forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.95,0:03:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.11,0:03:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be taken to the Tachibana residence someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.92,0:03:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I ignored you even though we lived together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be hard for us to separate if I fell in love with you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I always kept my feelings subdued so that I will be fine no matter when you leave, but there was no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.60,0:03:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't lie to myself any longer,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,so I've decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.39,0:03:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I was on my knees in front of the Tachibana residence the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, I had more patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:04:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided that I will do my best by myself and that I won't trouble anyone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.07,0:04:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, Misuzu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you really that sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.06,0:04:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that you just had a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Your feet won't move?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go see the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll probably get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the female doctor at the clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She can probably help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be healed in a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san and I discovered the reason for my illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.31,0:04:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My other self is in the sky, and she's carrying a burden by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why my body froze.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You always spout those fantasies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:05:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's keep on living like before, without bothering with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.54,0:05:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's live our respective lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.31,0:05:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep striving by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Why are you saying such things?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you angry because I left you alone for a long time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.97,0:05:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to go to the hospital, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.01,0:05:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take good care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But two is better than one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Misuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.28,0:05:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think? Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.32,0:05:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make it tasty next time, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want any.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Your cooking is never good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Children grow up eating their parents' cooking, even if it isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.18,0:06:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.99,0:06:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that you'll get sick too if you're friendly with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you dream that too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Misuzu,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not scared of any sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.54,0:06:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If I get sick, I'll be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.71,0:06:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's proof that we became friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It tastes good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.91,0:06:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.69,0:07:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should I cut it to?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave that up to you, Mummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.75,0:07:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll cut it to where you look your cutest, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mummy, you have more wrinkles now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to shave your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're young.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Once, at an open house, I was the only kid who was happy because everyone else's mums were old.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You were crying because you got the answer wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that I needed to be cool, so I raised my hand without knowing the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you hit me in front of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because you said "Gao", your favourite phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.58,0:07:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Discipline, discipline.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to that, Misuzu grew up into a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:07:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:08:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You've matured quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying that phrase less often now too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.87,0:08:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.27,0:08:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah well, it's easier this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just have to make it match.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.96,0:08:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the other side is too short!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.89,0:08:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I was able to balance both sides, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.79,0:08:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so short.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.78,0:09:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.80,0:09:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like a small child again,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mummy's child.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.31,0:09:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's redo everything from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's redo it together, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.05,0:09:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It starts from here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.53,0:09:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.82,0:09:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's almost the summer festival, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, that's right. I forgot that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I'll take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go to the beach after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,because I've never gone with you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.83,0:09:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You have so many places you want to visit, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to do many fun things with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.58,0:10:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, let's do lots of fun things together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's fill your diary up with fun things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.81,0:10:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Mummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.47,0:10:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll remember your smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always remember, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.65,0:10:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.86,0:10:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, Misuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu, you were awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.22,0:10:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still sleepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.37,0:10:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:56.42,Note,,0,0,0,,[Note: oba-san = an older woman whom one doesn't know well]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you, oba-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that we would work our hardest together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.55,0:11:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.62,0:11:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama went far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.74,0:11:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to remember stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.30,0:11:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your substitute mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,From today, I'll try to restore her memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.94,0:11:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right if I'm Haruko-obasan until the day you see me as your mother again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I borrowed this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, you can go outside with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts, and I can't walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what this wheelchair is for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.32,0:11:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:58.57,Note,,0,0,0,,[Note: Haruko refers to herself as "oba-san", showing her acceptance of the role]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll push you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.97,0:11:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more fun playing cards by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.33,0:12:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's play together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels good to be outside in the sun, and there are lots of fun things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind is blowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.89,0:12:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's blowing, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.64,0:12:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun is sizzling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The cicadas are chirping.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.31,0:12:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So much that it's almost noisy, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.25,0:12:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.77,0:12:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu, I'm your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that this girl can't be in large crowds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.43,0:12:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I left her with you in this quiet town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.11,0:12:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She is my child now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I already have your parents' permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She belongs to Ikuko and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the Kamio residence such a convenient place to drop her off when she's in the way and pick her up when you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't leave her with you, where she gets sicker.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:17.44,Note,,0,0,0,,[Note: He is being distant and formal by using the standard language]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop using that standard language!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hearing it disgusts me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oba-san, you're scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm sorry for yelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.31,0:13:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oba-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,T-That's not how it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a while ago she called me "Mummy" all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.01,0:13:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's go, Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Say "thank you" to Oba-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where's your "thank you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.35,0:13:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.35,0:13:40.59,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.99,0:13:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take Misuzu away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.81,0:13:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu was alone for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.69,0:13:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose fault was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it ours?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I decided to stay with her forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still going to push her around because of our arguments?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.34,0:13:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.55,0:14:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm uneducated, so I don't know how to sugarcoat it, but I know that I want to be with her much more than you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.50,0:14:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.34,0:14:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu, do you want to be with Haruko-obasan from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oba-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.38,0:14:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to keep living with her from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.98,0:14:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If she says at that time that she doesn't want to be with me anymore, then I won't mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't mind if you take Misuzu away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.31,0:14:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.86,0:14:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.28,0:14:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I regain the time that we've lost with just that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:53.95,Note,,0,0,0,,[Note: Haruko uses "-chan" to distance herself from Misuzu, just like an aunt]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu-chan, you really like dinosaurs, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a Maiasaura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It means "good mother dinosaur."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:14:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.16,0:15:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a Velociraptor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It means "speedy thief."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.11,0:15:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah! That one is like Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder which one of us is the thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.70,0:15:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It is,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's a short walk, so you'll have to bear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It should be cooler when we arrive at the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There, let's eat our boxed lunch,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the boxed lunch that I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.46,0:15:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Our lunch will be wasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.15,0:15:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There are sweet egg omelettes too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I made them at your request.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.49,0:15:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make it a fun day, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.11,0:15:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what's going to happen to the boxed lunch that I made?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then do whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:16:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to play by yourself that much, then go home by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.72,0:16:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.16,0:16:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Gao.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home, Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.73,0:16:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I've known this all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.94,0:16:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really not cut out to be a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:16:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What I've been doing isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.97,0:17:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu, what happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.31,0:17:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.79,0:17:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.64,0:17:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Cicada.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll get it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.50,0:17:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the cicada-getting-oba-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.34,0:17:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Cicada-getting-oba-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.22,0:17:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,A scaredy-cat like you needs one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.29,0:17:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You can play at ease now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.89,0:17:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.97,0:17:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:17:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right... for me to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't ask for too much anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.14,0:18:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right if I can just stay with you all day long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all that I wish for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is the day I promised Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That fool, he'll come to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'll answer that you want to go with him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll say that you don't want to be with me anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.67,0:18:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer vacation will still continue, but our time together ends today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.38,0:19:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.53,0:19:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.59,0:19:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Keisuke,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.57,0:19:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,there's one last place I want to take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have a bit more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.73,0:19:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu, it's the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.00,0:19:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We've come so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how many years it took for the two of us to come here together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.74,0:19:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We should have been able to see this beautiful scenery as often as we wanted; what exactly were we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it all right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.24,0:19:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She's heavy, since it's been a long time since you held her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.33,0:19:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to you that she was able to grow this big.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Give this to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.01,0:20:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She loves this stuffed animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she'll calm down and sleep if she holds this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.15,0:20:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If she still whines, have her drink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's her favourite juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.22,0:20:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.46,0:20:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The princess is leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.29,0:20:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Misu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.40,0:21:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.98,0:21:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.99,0:21:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, the two of them talked in the twilight for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.10,0:21:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll bring a doctor I can trust, so will you have her examined?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.12,0:21:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.34,0:22:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who was by Misuzu's side after all this time was...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.99,0:22:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...Misuzu's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.86,0:23:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I had wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.61,0:23:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They were pure white wings, and I was flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.44,0:23:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.54,0:23:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nice dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.35,0:23:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was a sad dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.58,0:23:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the saddest dream in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.02,0:23:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is the end of my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.80,0:24:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, I'm going to be by your side,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.59,0:24:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,always and forever.
